## amja alpla kde ak  navtabs ase konta war click kel tr active ahe ka nahi smjna sathi 
apn   routerLinkActive="router-link-active"  wa pr krto ya cha wapar krun
tab active ahe ka nahi check krun skto

## ani a tag href use nahi kryahc karan page refersh hoto tr direct apn routerlink use krych 

## ani ta yamde ajunn ak ahe smja routerLinkActive he apna application cha url war base ahe

exa - localhost:3000/contact 

tr url mde conact ahe tr conact link active hoiyil

## pm ya url mde localhost:3000 pn ahe he HOME Componet la point krto 

tr home Componet pn active hoyil tr tya sathi apn   [routerLinkActiveOptions]="{exact:true}" 
ya ch warp kelnae je router active ahe tyla ch active class apply hoyil 